âŒ Don'ts:
â†’ Type 1: tempting, but destroys historical accuracy
â†’ Type 3: a trap. Loses critical history between values

âœ… Do's:
â†’ Type 2 with START_DATE/END_DATE tracking
â†’ Tip: an IS_CURRENT column = debugging lifesaver


